    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "A crystalline sphere, swirling with constantly shifting constellations, sits atop a *lyrakien staff*, a silver shaft that sparkles with the gentle glow of starlight. Desnans first created the staves, inspired by the music- and freedom-loving lyrakien azatas, but these staves are popular with spellcasters of all faiths who like travel, art, or the stars. While wielding a *lyrakien staff*, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus on saving throws against incapacitation effects.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 103,
